## ğŸ“Œ Project Overview  
Customer churn is a critical problem for telecom companies. As a data scientist at **Neo Telecom**, the goal of this project is to analyze customer data, gain insights into churn patterns, and build predictive models to reduce customer attrition.  

This project involves **data manipulation, visualization, and machine learning models** (Linear Regression, Logistic Regression, Decision Tree, and Random Forest) to analyze and predict customer churn.  

