## ğŸ“¢ Results & Insights  
ğŸ”¹ Senior male citizens using **electronic check payments** have a higher churn rate.  
ğŸ”¹ Customers with **tenure > 70 months** or **monthly charges > $100** are more likely to churn.  
ğŸ”¹ Customers with **two-year contracts** and **mailed check payments** churn less frequently.  
ğŸ”¹ **Random Forest** achieved the highest accuracy in churn prediction.  

